flowchart LR
    BACKUP[Backup Scheduler]

    BACKUP --> SNAP[WAL / snapshot capture]
    SNAP --> ENCRYPT[encrypt backup]
    ENCRYPT --> STORE[(Object store\nS3 / GCS)]
    STORE --> XREG[cross-region copy]

    STORE --> RESTORE[restore trigger]
    RESTORE --> DECRYPT[decrypt + decompress]
    DECRYPT --> LOAD[load to target DB]
    LOAD --> VERIFY[verify checksums]
    VERIFY -->|fail| ALERT[alert + retry]
    VERIFY -->|pass| LIVE[service live on standby]
